  "title": "Abacus Teacher",
  "description": "<h3><strong>We're Hiring: Mental Arithmetic Teacher</strong></h3>\n<p>Are you passionate about working with children and helping them develop strong math and cognitive skills? Join our team at <strong>CMA Mental Arithmetic Toa Payoh</strong>, where we nurture young minds through innovative mental arithmetic and abacus training.</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct Abacus and Mental Arithmetic classes using our structured video-based teaching tools.</li>\n  <li>Supervise, guide, and motivate students throughout their learning journey.</li>\n  <li>Engage actively with students and parents to share progress and provide support.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Genuine passion for teaching and working with children.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication skills and a solid foundation in mathematics.</li>\n  <li>Able to connect well with preschool and primary school students.</li>\n  <li>Energetic, responsible, and committed with a positive work attitude.</li>\n  <li>Available to work:<br>\n<strong>Wednesday to Friday: 1:00 PM – 9:00 PM<br>\nWeekends: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM</strong></li>\n  <li>Abacus knowledge is a bonus, but not required—<strong>comprehensive training will be provided</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in teaching or working with children is an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What We Offer:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Training and certification in CMA’s unique teaching methodology</li>\n  <li>Supportive and collaborative working environment</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for professional growth</li>\n  <li>Competitive salary (commensurate with experience and qualifications)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you're enthusiastic about education and want to make a difference in children's lives, <strong>we’d love to hear from you!</strong></p>",
