    "uen": "200718635M",
    "description": "<p>Welcome to CMA Mental Arithmetic Toa Payoh, a trusted learning center dedicated to nurturing young minds through the power of mental arithmetic. As part of the internationally recognized CMA (Complete Mental Arithmetic) network, we specialize in a unique dual-hand abacus technique that stimulates both the left and right hemispheres of the brain—enhancing concentration, memory, creativity, and confidence in children.<br>\n<br>\nLocated in the heart of Toa Payoh, our center provides a supportive and engaging environment where students aged 3 to 12 develop strong mathematical foundations and essential cognitive skills. Our experienced and passionate instructors are committed to helping each child reach their full potential through a structured, fun, and results-driven curriculum.<br>\n<br>\nAt CMA Toa Payoh, we believe every child can excel in math and beyond—with the right guidance and tools. Join us on a transformative learning journey where mental arithmetic becomes more than just numbers—it becomes a lifelong advantage.</p>",
